title: Scott Morrison | Biography, Education, & Previous Offices | Britannica
snippet: Scott Morrison (born May 13, 1968, Bronte, New South Wales, Australia) is an Australian conservative politician who served as leader of the Liberal Party and prime minister of Australia (2018–22).
